title: Veggie quiche
ingredients: ['110g grated Monterrey Jack cheese', '70g chopped kale', '150g chopped red and yellow onion', '125g plain flour', '60g whole wheat pastry flour', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '100g lard', '8 tablespoons cold water, or as needed', '500ml semi-skimmed milk', '3 eggs', '3 tablespoons plain flour', '1 teaspoon baking powder', '1/2 teaspoon salt']
